                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5511" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0886</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9023 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">养鲜界的洞天鲜境——容声WILL冰箱的诞生之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Wonderland of freshness domain ——The birth of Ronshen WILL refrigerators</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马宝龙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信家电集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">23 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">容声；WILL养鲜冰箱；新产品开发理论；4Ps理论 ；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ronshen;“WILL”refrigerator; New Product Development;4Ps Theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着生活水平提高和消费需求的升级，人们开始追求更高品质更健康的冰箱产品，消费者对冰箱的认知已经从基本的贮藏机器升级到了更品质化的健康管理设备。然而，市面上现存冰箱却无法满足这些需求，冰箱消费者的痛点急需解决。在这一背景下，容声品牌携新开发出的WILL养鲜冰鲜于众多同类产品中脱颖而出，获得多项业界大奖的同时，也收到广大消费者的如潮好评。本案例描述了容声WILL养鲜冰箱从创意诞生、筛选、技术研发、产品落地到市场推广各阶段的关键决策过程，剖析了容声WILL养鲜冰箱的开发动因、概念选择及阶段策略。本案例旨在帮助学生深刻理解新产品开发等相关的理论知识，指导学生学习关于企业开发新产品的策略选择、关键任务及营销措施落地等相关问题的决策工具和分析方法。 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the improvement of living standard and the upgrading of consumption demand, people began to pursue refrigerator products of higher quality and healthier contributes. Consumers&#39; cognition of refrigerator has been upgraded from basic storage machine to more quality health management equipment. However, the existing refrigerators fail to meet these needs, and the pain points of refrigerator consumers need to be solved urgently. In this context, Ronshen, with the newly developed WILL refrigerator product which stands out among similar products, has won many awards, and also received the popularity of consumers. This case describes the key decision-making process of the Ronshen WILL refrigerator from the birth, screening of originality, technology research and development, product landing to marketing promotion, and analyzes the development motivation, originality concept selection and supporting strategies of the refrigerator. This case aims to help students understand the theoretical knowledge of the new product development of a brand and guides them to learn decision tools and analysis methods on the strategic choice, key tasks and marketing measures implementation of new products development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《产品开发管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新产品开发理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-09</td>
                            </tr>
